{"tid":847179,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"送名錶俾阿媽女友發爛渣 命苦港男 ：男人就咁慘！","createTime":"2018-10-04T03:41:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T08:02:21.000Z","uid":58335,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"235bef0da87a0d17cd5e4d82f552a1e4927acf65","tid":847179,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T03:41:37.000Z","msg":"港女真係臭雞黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20181002/large/1538473642_f761.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20181002%2Flarge%2F1538473642_f761.jpg&h=bd7e9443&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n25歲的James（化名），早前用了半年時間儲錢，買了一隻價值約47000元的勞力士手錶，給母親作生日禮物，上周向相識五個月的女友提及此事，女友反問：「咁我有冇份？」<br />\n<br />\nJames如實告訴女友，指積蓄都花光在送給母親的禮物上，沒有多餘錢再買一隻給女朋友，對方隨即表現冷淡，之後五、六日都不時提起這個話題，令James大感無奈。<br />\n<br />\n他將經歷分享到互聯網，隨即引來熱烈討論。有網民大讚James孝順，反之女友想法幼稚，應早點分手。不過亦有網民認為，男方只要改善表達的方式，便可化解與女朋友的紛爭。<br />\n<br />\nJames指自己一向以家人為先，所以希望伴侶能與他的家人融洽相處，否則勉強下去都沒有什麼意思。他認為，今次事件不會影響他與女朋友的關係，當笑話一則，不過若對方將事件放在心上，「可能她看物質比較重，如果她需要物質多過我，那我未必會選擇她。」<br />\n<br />\n這宗女友與母親的糾紛，各人有不同的說法。<br />\n<br />\n「男人一出世就咁慘！」港男Jason大嘆作為男性，經常會夾在父母和伴侶中間，成為磨心，如果遇到事主的情況，只好再努力儲錢，多買一份禮物給女朋友以消怒火。Edmond亦認為，男方要負責伴侶所有支出的情況在香港較為常見，指女方的價值觀都是想男方負責所有支出，包括雙方家庭的花費。<br />\n<br />\n不過，林小姐認為，男友有能力送名貴禮物給母親，是孝順的表現，亦會替他高興，不會因為自己沒有禮物而生氣。<br />\n<br />\n至於送禮物的習慣，鍾小姐說不一定要收名貴禮物，最重要的還是心意；宋小姐則認為送禮要視乎雙方的經濟能力，笑言：「男朋友愛我便可以。」<br />\n<br />\n撰文：亦安<br />\n<br />\n攝影：李育明<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20181003/628126?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20181003%2F628126%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=%2FYputimRECP4bxIM%2BUTwTx4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=adb1837b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20181003%2F628126%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=ff44da2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20181003/628126?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_social_nextmagazinefansclub&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"aa0c219d5a346050f63a0267badc08db24a5f656","tid":847179,"uid":29080,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T03:44:51.000Z","msg":"答佢：你而家冇但係你將來會有"},{"pid":"4cc78217060d98c629b06417648229f5d1c255be","tid":847179,"uid":125213,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T03:47:02.000Z","msg":"呢啲八婆就飛撚咗佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91a29f8b8baf5aa046572fb99233489622114a07","tid":847179,"uid":143192,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T03:48:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/04/114853_0b561a574a10f8b9e221d7627b16cb59.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F04%2F114853_0b561a574a10f8b9e221d7627b16cb59.png&h=0a5c8c04&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e730bbdf8b104e8451912f7e7b9ecdbc8cf2c00","tid":847179,"uid":76063,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T03:50:33.000Z","msg":"阿媽得一個"},{"pid":"9341308b9343a98d84128ec48c660a73c83575f1","tid":847179,"uid":96007,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T03:51:13.000Z","msg":"（80kg暗瘡肥髮月入8k但我有內在美）高登仔：抵啦 貪人靚痴埋啲港女做女友，唔搵個普通嘅女仔做女朋友"},{"pid":"0f00347c56f619de2b63d1a228f6f7c49f6d61b6","tid":847179,"uid":16061,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20